Prepare bash for Windows Terminal
----------------------------------

Install Windows Terminal Preview
---------------------------------
On Microsoft Store install Windows Terminal Preview

Install Windows Subsystem for Linux
--------------------------------------
Run Windows PowerShell with admin
On the PowerShell
$ Enable-WindowsOptionalFeature -Online -FeatureName Microsoft-Windows-Subsystem-Linux
answer 'Y' and reboot system

Install Ubuntu
---------------
On Microsoft Store install Ubuntu 22.04.2 LTS
as Windows Subsystem for Linux (WSL)
Press 'Get' to download
Press 'Open' to install
Enter new UNIX username: jedywei
New password: iamarock

done the Windows Subsystem for Linux with Ubuntu installation




